items.sentence: I don't think that you should do that with Tom.
I don't think that you need to worry about Tom.
I don't think that Tom would help Mary do that.
I don't think that Tom would forget to do that.
I don't think that Tom will be at home tonight.
I don't think Tom was the first one here today.
I don't think that it's fair to single out Tom.
I don't think Tom knows what I do for a living.
I don't think Tom knows I'm not single anymore.
I don't think Tom knows how many cats Mary has.
